  <h1>Pizza</h1>
  <img src="images/pizza.jpg" alt="Pizza">
  <h2> Description </h2>
  <p> This pizza is Mara's favorite as it is is rich with colorful ingrediants. The flavors create a 
      bomb in the palate.</p>
  <h3> Ingredients </h3>
     <ul>
       <li> 1 ready made pizza crust</li>
       <li> 2 cups shredded mozzarella cheese</li>
       <li> 1 cup tomato sauce</li>
       <li> 1/2 cup chopped green bell pepper</li>
       <li> 1/2 cup fresh sliced mushrooms</li>
       <li> 4 cups of jalapeno</li>
       <li> 2 cups of fried bacon</li>
    </ul>
       
  <h3>Steps </h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Pat dry chicken </li>
      <li>Heat oil and butter in pan</li>
      <li>Take out chicken and add tomato sauce </li>
      <li>Add whole tomatoes, wine, basil, oregano, garlic, parsley, salt and pepper</li>
      <li>Simmer covered for 45-50 minutes,until chicken is tender</li>
      li>Combine flour with 3 teaspoons of water, stir into sauce </li>
      <li>Cook for another 10 minutes, until sauce is thickened</li>
            
       
  
